{
  "chapter": "115",
  "title": "朝鲜列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "卫满立朝鲜",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫满\">满（卫满）</span>，原是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国人。当初<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国最强盛的时候，曾经攻略使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">真番</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>归属自己，为之设置官吏，修筑边塞障塞。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国后，这里归属<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>郡的外徼。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴起时，因为这里偏远难以守卫，就重新修治<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>的旧塞，以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浿水</span>为界，归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>反叛，逃入<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫满\">满（卫满）</span>也流亡出走，聚集党徒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀人</span>，梳成椎形发髻、穿<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>衣服向东逃出边塞，渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浿水</span>，居住在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝原来的空地上下障塞，渐渐役使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">真番</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>的<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>以及原来<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的流亡者使之归属，自立为王，定都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">王险</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "正逢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span>帝、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span>时期<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>初定，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">辽东太守</span>就与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫满\">满（卫满）</span>约定，让他做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的外<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，保护塞外的<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>，不让他们侵扰边境；各<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>想入朝觐见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的，不得禁止。太守上报后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>答应了，因此<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫满\">满（卫满）</span>得以凭借兵威和财物侵犯降服周围的小城邑，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">真番</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">临屯</span>都来服属，所辖方圆有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千里</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "右渠拒汉",
      "text": "王位传到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>、再传到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>时，所引诱的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝流亡之人越来越多，而且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>从未入朝觐见；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">真番</span>周围诸国想要上书觐见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>又拥塞道路不让他们通过。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元封二年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">涉何</span>去责让劝谕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>始终不肯接受诏命。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：涉何\">何（涉何）</span>离开到了边界上，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浿水</span>边，让自己的随从<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>送<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：涉何\">何（涉何）</span>的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">裨王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：裨王长\">长（裨王长）</span>，当即渡水，飞驰入塞，回去报告<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>说：\"<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将</span>领。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>认为他名头好听，就不加追究，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：涉何\">何（涉何）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">辽东东部都尉</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>怨恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：涉何\">何（涉何）</span>，发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：涉何\">何（涉何）</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "汉军征朝鲜",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>招募<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">罪人</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>。那年秋天，派遣<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨仆</span>从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地浮<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渤海</span>出发；兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五万人</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荀彘</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>出发：讨伐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>发兵据守险要。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卒正</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卒正多\">多（卒正多）</span>率领<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>兵先出击，战败溃散，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卒正多\">多（卒正多）</span>逃回，因<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">坐法</span>被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span>率<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七千人</span>先到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">王险</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>守城，察觉到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>军人少，就出城<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>军败散逃走。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨仆</span>失去部众，在山中躲藏了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十馀日（时长）</span>，渐渐搜求收拢溃散士卒，重又聚集起来。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浿水</span>西岸的军队，未能从前面<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>阵。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>因为两位将军没有取得胜利，就派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫山</span>借助兵威前去劝谕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>见到使者后叩头谢罪：\"愿意投降，只是担心两位将军诈<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>；如今看到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">信节</span>，请求服降。\" 派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>入朝谢罪，献上<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千匹</span>，以及馈赠<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">军粮</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人众</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀</span>，持兵器，正要渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浿水</span>，使者和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>怀疑他们会发生变故，对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>说既已服降，应当命令众人不要持兵器。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>也怀疑使者和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>要诈<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>自己，于是不渡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浿水</span>，又带兵返回。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫山\">山（卫山）</span>回去向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>报告，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫山\">山（卫山）</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浿水</span>上的军队，于是前进，到城下，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻西北方向。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>军也前来会合，驻扎在城南。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>坚守城池，数月都未能攻下。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "两将不和",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>一向是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侍中</span>，受宠，率领<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>的士卒，彪悍，乘胜进攻，军中多骄傲。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>率领<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>卒，入海作战，本来已多次战败逃亡；此前与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，因而受辱折损士卒，士卒都很恐惧，主将心中惭愧，在<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>时，常持议和之<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>猛烈<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>就暗中派使者私下与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>约降，使者往来商谈，尚未肯决定。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>数次与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>约期<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>斗，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>想急于达成私下的约降，不赴约；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>也派人寻求机会劝降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>不肯，心里归附<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>：因此两位将军互不相容。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>心里猜疑<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>之前有损失军队的罪过，现在又与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>私下交好却又不投降，怀疑他有反叛的计划，没敢发作。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将率</span>不能胜任，之前派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫山</span>去劝谕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>投降，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫山\">山（卫山）</span>作为使者不能独断决事，又与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>谋算失误，最终破坏了约定。如今两位将军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻城池，又意见相左，所以长久不能决胜。于是派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">济南太守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙遂</span>前去，凡有便宜可以从事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙遂\">遂（公孙遂）</span>到了，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>本应早就攻下，没有攻下是有原因的。\" 说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>数次不赴约，把一向所怀疑的事都告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙遂\">遂（公孙遂）</span>，说：\"如今这样不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>行动，恐怕会成大祸，不只是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>的问题，还将与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>共同消灭我军。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙遂\">遂（公孙遂）</span>也认为是这样，就用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>召<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span>进入<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>营议事，立即命<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>的部下逮捕<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span>，合并了他的军队，上报<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙遂\">遂（公孙遂）</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "右渠被杀平朝鲜",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>已合并两军，就猛烈<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">路人</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩阴</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尼谿相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：尼谿参\">参（尼谿参）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夹</span>互相商议说：\"起初想投降<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>现在被擒，只有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>合并指挥，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>事愈加急迫，恐怕无法抵挡，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王</span>又不肯投降。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩阴\">阴（韩阴）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王唊\">唊（王唊）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">路人</span>都逃亡归降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">路人</span>途中死去。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元封三年夏</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尼谿相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：尼谿参\">参（尼谿参）</span>派人<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>前来投降。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">王险</span>城还未攻下，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>原先的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成巳</span>又反叛，再次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打官吏。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：右渠子长\">长（右渠子长）</span>降、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">路人</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：路人子最\">最（路人子最）</span>告谕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成巳</span>，因此终于平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>，设置为四郡。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：尼谿参\">参（尼谿参）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">澅清侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩阴\">阴（韩阴）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">荻苴侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王唊\">唊（王唊）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平州侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：右渠子长\">长（右渠子长）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">几侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：路人子最\">最（路人子最）</span>因<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲死国且颇有功劳，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">温阳侯</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>被征召回京，因争功相嫉、谋划乖谬，被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">弃市</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船将军</span>也因军队到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洌口</span>，应当等待<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span>，却擅自先行出击，损失伤亡很多，应当<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">赎为</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "太史公论赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>依恃险固，国家因此断绝了祭祀。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">涉何</span>虚报战功，成为战事的开端。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楼船</span>将领心胸狭隘，遇难招致罪咎。 悔恨失去了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番禺</span>之功，反而遭到猜疑。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荀彘</span>争功邀劳，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙遂\">遂（公孙遂）</span>都被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀。 两支军队都蒙受耻辱，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将率</span>没有一人得以封侯。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫满</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>人，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>是其王国。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">王险</span>建为都城，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">路人</span>任为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">右渠</span>首先出错，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">涉何</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>奏。 祸端从此而起，二将迷于狐疑。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫山\">山（卫山）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙遂\">遂（公孙遂）</span>伏法，纷乱无状。"
    }
  }
}